errtee add:
	2016-01-04:
	bugfixes
	========
	resize window to 0 -> stack trace
	select in options menu -> mouse mode = 0

	improvements
	============
	a grid is shown

	all shortcuts work
	  'A';AntennaElm
	  'a';OpAmpElm
	  'c';CapacitorElm
	  'd';DiodeElm
	  'f';NMosfetElm
	  'g';GroundElm
	  'i';CurrentElm
	  'I';InverterElm
	  'j';NJfetElm
	  'l';InductorElm
